i recently had this problem. Heres what you do.

Search for “playerismember” in client.java (without the “” of course)

delete every item under the one that lists items under it.

Then just search through your client and delete that part of the commands for the rest of the stuff.

Theres really no way to explain it that well you just have to use common sence.
